            "icon": "book_5",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>No. Each of the 12 steps is grounded in <strong>real research, current AI trends, and actual events</strong> happening today. Nothing here is science fiction, it’s the uncomfortable reality unfolding around us.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
