            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>You <em>could</em> spend months digging through scattered blogs, podcasts, and conspiracy threads. But this ebook <strong>compresses everything into one clear framework</strong>, saving you time, giving you structure, and showing you the full picture you won’t find anywhere else.</p>",
