            "post_author_verified": false,
            "post_time": "14d ago",
            "post_text": "<p>I’m 58 years old and not tech savvy but even I can see something is VERY wrong. cascade 10 about the banks and social credit system? My daughter in Seattle just told me her apartment building installed facial recognition that’s “optional” but you get rent discount if you opt in 🎉🎉🎉 Bought 5 copies of this book on amazon one for each of my kids. They think mom’s gone down the rabbit hole but when cascade 12 hits, they’ll thank me. God bless you for exposing this. Praying more people wake up before it’s too late 🙏✝️</p>",
