            "post_text": "<p>Guys… I’m a truck driver, 44 years old, and Cascade 5 about autonomous vehicles hit way too close to home. They told us we had “at least 10 years” before self-driving trucks. BS. My buddy at FedEx just sent me pics of their new AI fleet in testing – NO DRIVERS.</p>",
