    "trustpilot_reviews_7JBRMA": {
      "type": "trustpilot-reviews",
      "blocks": {
        "column_kGEcQa": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "star_color": "#00b67a",
            "bg_star_color": "#c8c8c8",
            "star_symbol_color": "#ffffff",
            "stars_rating": 5,
            "title": "Finally, someone connected ALL the dots",
            "text": "<p>I've been following AI development for years, watching YouTube videos, reading forums, always feeling like I was only getting pieces of the puzzle. This book? It's the full picture. The chapter on the Pentagon's classified AI projects literally made my jaw drop. My wife thought I was paranoid about our smart home devices after reading the surveillance section together, we've completely reorganized our digital life. Worth every penny and then some.</p>",
            "author": "James M."
          }
        },
        "column_DmcAHe": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "star_color": "#00b67a",
            "bg_star_color": "#c8c8c8",
            "star_symbol_color": "#ffffff",
            "stars_rating": 5,
            "title": "Saved my career – seriously",
            "text": "<p>I'm 43, work in logistics, and have been losing sleep about automation. The cascade 3 didn't just confirm my fears, it gave me a roadmap. Already enrolled in one of the \"safe career\" transitions the book recommends. My only regret is not finding this sooner. If you're worried about your job, stop scrolling Twitter for answers and GET THIS BOOK.</p>",
            "author": "<em>Anthony R.</em>"
          }
        },
        "column_qwrWJR": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "star_color": "#00b67a",
            "bg_star_color": "#c8c8c8",
            "star_symbol_color": "#ffffff",
            "stars_rating": 5,
            "title": "The children chapter changed everything",
            "text": "<p>As a mother of two teens, the section on AI's impact on children hit me like a truck. I had NO IDEA about the \"cognitive restructuring\" happening through AI companions. We've implemented the family protection strategies from Chapter 7, and I'm already seeing positive changes in my kids' behavior and focus. This isn't fear-mongering – it's a wake-up call every parent needs.</p>",
            "author": "Sarah K."
          }
        },
        "column_b3kXcd": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "star_color": "#00b67a",
            "bg_star_color": "#c8c8c8",
            "star_symbol_color": "#ffffff",
            "stars_rating": 5,
            "title": "I work in tech. This book is terrifyingly accurate",
            "text": "<p>Without violating my NDA, let me just say: the author knows things. The details about OpenAI's pivot to secrecy, the real reasons behind the tech layoffs, the actual AGI timeline – it's all true. I've been in the industry for 15 years and this book connected dots I didn't even know existed. Already bought copies for my family members. They need to know what's coming.</p>",
            "author": "DevGuy2019"
          }
        },
        "column_a9MtRd": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "star_color": "#00b67a",
            "bg_star_color": "#c8c8c8",
            "star_symbol_color": "#ffffff",
            "stars_rating": 5,
            "title": "From skeptic to believer in 150+ pages",
            "text": "<p>My son recommended this book. I thought he was getting too deep into conspiracy theories. Then I read it. The government documents, the timeline correlations, the whistleblower testimonies, it's all documented. Not theories, FACTS. The section on deepfakes and the elections made me physically nauseous because I remembered those news stories differently. We've been played, folks.</p>",
            "author": "Michael T."
          }
        },
        "column_3eErAf": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "star_color": "#00b67a",
            "bg_star_color": "#c8c8c8",
            "star_symbol_color": "#ffffff",
            "stars_rating": 5,
            "title": "The survival guide alone is worth 10x the price",
            "text": "<p>I've read dozens of books on future threats, but none provided actionable steps like this. The \"AI Survival Guide\" in the final chapters isn't just theory, it's a practical playbook. Already implemented the financial protection strategies and the \"analog advantage\" techniques. My family went from anxious to prepared. This is the manual for navigating what's coming.</p>",
            "author": "PrepperDad_Colorado"
          }
        },
        "column_3JXTLd": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "star_color": "#00b67a",
            "bg_star_color": "#c8c8c8",
            "star_symbol_color": "#ffffff",
            "stars_rating": 5,
            "title": "Explains EVERYTHING happening right now",
            "text": "<p>Remember feeling like something was \"off\" about the world lately? This book explains why. The Dead Internet Theory chapter made me audit my social media, found 7 bot accounts I'd been interacting with regularly thinking they were real people. The manipulation is already here. Thank God someone finally had the courage to expose all of this.</p>",
            "author": "Lisa W."
          }
        },
        "column_LiLVPk": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "star_color": "#00b67a",
            "bg_star_color": "#c8c8c8",
            "star_symbol_color": "#ffffff",
            "stars_rating": 5,
            "title": "Couldn't put it down – read it in one night",
            "text": "<p>Started reading at 9 PM, finished at 4 AM. Could. Not. Stop. Every chapter revealed another layer of the deception. The connection between AI development and recent global events is undeniable once you see it laid out. My group chat hasn't stopped discussing this book for two weeks. It's that important.</p>",
            "author": "TruthSeeker_88"
          }
        },
        "column_KDDqXi": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "star_color": "#00b67a",
            "bg_star_color": "#c8c8c8",
            "star_symbol_color": "#ffffff",
            "stars_rating": 5,
            "title": "The whistleblower interviews… WOW",
            "text": "<p>The three anonymous Big Tech whistleblower interviews scattered throughout the book are EXPLOSIVE. Especially the one from the OpenAI insider. Now I understand why GPT-4's release was so different, why certain features were hidden, and what they're really building toward. This information needs to be mainstream news, but we know why it isn't.</p>",
            "author": "Jennifer P."
          }
        }
      },
